308
00:24:23,136 --> 00:24:25,970
[faint moaning]

309
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:31,389
[faint howling]

310
00:24:54,668 --> 00:24:57,160
[faint moaning]

311
00:25:04,302 --> 00:25:06,544
[water trickling]

312
00:25:37,377 --> 00:25:39,835
[trickling continues]

313
