[gasps]

314
00:25:41,757 --> 00:25:45,046
[sighs] You scared
the hell out of me.

315
00:25:45,135 --> 00:25:48,924
- What are you doing down here?
- I... I thought I heard something.

316
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:51,051
It sounded...

317
00:25:52,976 --> 00:25:54,558
It sounded like Ernest.

318
00:25:56,396 --> 00:25:58,433
Come on. Come away from there.

319
00:26:05,864 --> 00:26:07,105
Stay with me tonight.

320
00:26:08,700 --> 00:26:11,020
- Jess, you gotta get a hold of yourself.
- Robert, please.

321
00:26:11,078 --> 00:26:15,072
I can't be alone here anymore.
I can't stand being alone here.

322
00:26:16,792 --> 00:26:20,206
- All right. I'll stay.
- [siren wailing in distance]

323
