00:36:10,385 --> 00:36:12,001
[boy speaks, indistinct]

436
00:36:12,095 --> 00:36:15,008
[girl] Oh, yeah? There is
no such thing as monsters.

437
00:36:15,515 --> 00:36:17,802
- [growling]
- [screams playfully]

438
00:36:17,892 --> 00:36:20,225
- [growling]
- [screaming]

439
00:36:33,074 --> 00:36:34,406
Are you comfortable?

440
00:36:36,202 --> 00:36:38,034
[Ernest] Yes.

441
00:36:39,414 --> 00:36:42,248
Do you have any more pain?

442
00:36:42,792 --> 00:36:44,203
[Ernest] No.

443
00:36:44,711 --> 00:36:46,498
No pain.

444
00:36:47,255 --> 00:36:48,666
[button clicks]

445
00:36:50,675 --> 00:36:53,543
- [clicks]
