449
00:37:06,524 --> 00:37:08,015
[Robert]
Where are you, Valdemar?

450
00:37:10,945 --> 00:37:12,527
Can you see anything?
Can you...

451
00:37:13,990 --> 00:37:17,734
- tell me what you see?
